Job Description:We are seeking for the passionate, young and bold.Tertiary students who are keen to be part of a leading global advertising agency may apply to join our account servicing team.Interns will be trained in the area of client services, including conducting research, participating in brainstorming, preparing client presentation and execution of campaigns (online and offline). Requirements:• Candidate must be currently pursuing at least a Diploma or Bachelor's Degree in Communications/Marketing/ Business Studies or  equivalent• Fresh graduates who are keen on embarking a career in advertising are more than welcomed to join us• Creative, diligent, determined, self-starter and collaborative folks are welcomed • Effective spoken and written communications in English is required
Please apply for this position by sending your CV to hr@publicis.com.sg.
Applicants must indicate the period of time available for internship. We prefer candidates who are available for a minimum of 2 to 3 month period.
Kindly note that only shortlisted candidates will be notified.
